{"tid":666711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"9歲女童匯款5萬予主播　直播平台：無法證明由未成年人操作拒退款","createTime":"2018-05-16T06:15:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T07:20:26.000Z","uid":39464,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0fdfa6d9e0cc2a8c42028088b222b7c758f95886","tid":666711,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:15:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180516/s00004/08fe0221e80b9f3269bebc0d4e6b3a0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180516%2Fs00004%2F08fe0221e80b9f3269bebc0d4e6b3a0c.jpg&h=d9790159&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遼寧大連一名9歲女童，早前使用「虎牙直播」看節目，以網上支付平台向主播匯款逾5萬人民幣（約為6.2萬港元），其母事後追討3個多月不果。虎牙公關部回應，事主未能提供影片等資料，證明匯款操作由小孩進行，因此申訴未能通過審核。<br />\n<br />\n虎牙強調，只要有足夠證明是由未成年人操作匯款，公司會根據實際情況安排退款，此前亦有案例，但稱「雖然平台很人性化，但在前期審核方面還是非常嚴謹」，以免一些別有用心者利用。<br />\n<br />\n不少主播均以直播作為賺錢工具，而小孩取用父母戶口匯款事件，時有發生。今年1月，大連一名9歲孩童利用父親支付寶帳戶，先後向「快手直播」匯款逾30次，總共涉及5.8萬人民幣（約7.1萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180516/s00004/1526446579409\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180516%2Fs00004%2F1526446579409&d=71H6aUdLW1dRq8EZX0xA2cmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=f2a60cd6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180516%2Fs00004%2F1526446579409&h=4b070eea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180516/s00004/1526446579409</a>"},{"pid":"001c4b41338f84c9766fe35d1ee921cb734f9c5e","tid":666711,"uid":113626,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:17:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之前有個拎醫藥費去捐"},{"pid":"fef6e121d7f4e58287e4d44c6f53896b9d8efdf0","tid":666711,"uid":179467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:18:20.000Z","msg":"又一個ChargebackBoyz <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7db53f96afde8f2af2e03b7fa65a8222fdd8dbb1","tid":666711,"uid":2566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:18:29.000Z","msg":"真係好搵"},{"pid":"e3f9dd49186dbbbf6fea5e0a69f8aa5eefc2b159","tid":666711,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:20:46.000Z","msg":"支付寶夠方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8384bdda29c1ae72f5b41a841bec45166c2c2e5a","tid":666711,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:47:18.000Z","msg":"肯定比人打到飛起"},{"pid":"ca518806d47fda222137517351b203af3b50511f","tid":666711,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8384bdda29c1ae72f5b41a841bec45166c2c2e5a","tid":666711,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:47:18.000Z","msg":"肯定比人打到飛起"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:49:33.000Z","msg":"大連一名9歲孩童利用父親支付寶帳戶<br />\n<br />\n打死個老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3632a49859f95df42f89da0316e445c82ceb044","tid":666711,"uid":104106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T07:20:26.000Z","msg":"打機直播都夠膽收錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}